TranslatedText: Allow an application to manipulate audio settings during call.

TranslatedText: Allow an application to manipulate phone related audio settings.

TranslatedText: Allow an application to read call state.

OriginalText: Allow an application to record calls.
TranslatedText: Allow an application to record calls.

OriginalText: Allow applications to access various network features.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmerne får adgang til forskellige netværksfunktioner.

OriginalText: Allow applications to do things that can cost you money.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program kan gøre ting, som kan koste penge.

OriginalText: Allows an application to add or change the events on your calendar, which may send email to guests. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your calendar events or to send email to guests.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program tilføjer eller ændrer begivenhederne i din kalender, hvilket kan sende e-mail til gæster. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at slette eller ændre dine kalenderbegivenheder eller til at sende e-mail til gæster.

OriginalText: Allows an application to broadcast a notification that a WAP PUSH message has been received. Malicious applications may use this to forge MMS message receipt or to silently replace the content of any web page with malicious variants.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program udsender en meddelelse om, at der er modtaget en WAP PUSH-besked. Ondsindede programmer kan eventuelt bruge dette til at forfalske modtagelse af mms-besked eller i det skjulte erstatte indholdet på alle websider med ondsindede varianter.

OriginalText: Allows an application to broadcast a notification that an application package has been removed. Malicious applications may use this to kill any other running application.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program udsender en meddelelse om, at en programpakke er fjernet. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at afslutte et andet kørende program.

OriginalText: Allows an application to broadcast a notification that an SMS message has been received. Malicious applications may use this to forge incoming SMS messages.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program udsender en meddelelse om, at der er modtaget en sms-besked. Ondsindede programmer kan eventuelt bruge dette til at forfalske indgående sms-beskeder.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the background data usage setting.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer brugerindstillingerne for baggrundsdata.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the current configuration, such as the locale or overall font size.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer den nuværende konfiguration, f.eks. den lokale eller overordnede skrifttypestørrelse.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the global animation speed (faster or slower animations) at any time.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program altid kan ændre den globale animationshastighed (hurtigere eller langsommere animationer).

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the phone\'s clock time.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer telefonens klokkeslæt.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the phone\'s time zone.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer telefonens tidszone.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the rotation of the screen at any time. Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer rotationen af skærmen når som helst. Bør aldrig være nødvendigt til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the state of network connectivity.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer netværksforbindelsens tilstand.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change the state of tethered network connectivity.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer tilstand for et bundet netværk.

OriginalText: Allows an application to change whether a component of another application is enabled or not. Malicious applications can use this to disable important phone capabilities. Care must be used with permission, as it is possible to get application components into an unusable, inconsistent, or unstable state.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer, om en komponent fra et andet program er aktiveret eller ej. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at deaktivere vigtige telefonfunktioner. Denne tilladelse skal anvendes med forsigtighed, da det kan forårsage ubrugelige, inkonsekvente eller ustabile programkomponenter.

OriginalText: Allows an application to clear user data.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program rydder brugerdata.

OriginalText: Allows an application to communicate with Near Field Communication (NFC) tags, cards, and readers.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at kommunikere med Near Field Communication (NFC) tags, kort, og læsere

OriginalText: Allows an application to completely reset the system to its factory settings, erasing all data, configuration, and installed applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program nulstiller systemet fuldstændig til fabriksindstillingerne, sletter alle data, konfigurationer og installerede programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to configure the local Bluetooth phone, and to discover and pair with remote devices.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program konfigurerer den lokale Bluetooth-telefon samt opdager og parrer med fjerne enheder.

OriginalText: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points, and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program opretter og afbryder forbindelsen fra Wi-Fi-adgangspunkter og foretager ændringer i konfigurerede Wi-Fi-netværk.

OriginalText: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from WiMAX network.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at forbinde og afbryde forbindelsen til WiMAX netværk.

OriginalText: Allows an application to control the maximum number of processes that will run. Never needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program kontrollerer det maksimale antal processer, der kan køre. Er aldrig nødvendigt til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to control whether activities are always finished as soon as they go to the background. Never needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program kontrollerer, om aktiviteter altid afsluttes, så snart de går i baggrunden. Aldrig nødvendigt til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to create network sockets.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program opretter netværks-sockets.

OriginalText: Allows an application to delete Android packages. Malicious applications can use this to delete important applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program sletter Android-pakker. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at slette vigtige programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to delete cache files.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program sletter cachefiler.

OriginalText: Allows an application to deliver its own input events (key presses, etc.) to other applications. Malicious applications can use this to take over the phone.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program leverer sine egne inputbegivenheder (tastetryk osv.) til andre programmer. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at overtage telefonen.

OriginalText: Allows an application to disable the keylock and any associated password security. A legitimate example of this is the phone disabling the keylock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enabling the keylock when the call is finished.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program deaktiverer tastaturlåsen og al associeret adgangskodesikkerhed. Et legitimt eksempel på dette er, at telefonen deaktiverer tastaturlåsen, når der modtages et indgående telefonopkald, og genaktiverer tastaturlåsen, når opkaldet er afsluttet.

OriginalText: Allows an application to enable the car mode.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at aktivere biltilstand.

OriginalText: Allows an application to force any activity that is in the foreground to close and go back. Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program tvinger alle programmer, der er i forgrunden, til at lukke og køre i baggrunden. Bør aldrig være nødvendigt til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to forcibly stop other applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program tvangsstopper andre programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to free phone storage by deleting files in application cache directory. Access is very restricted usually to system process.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program frigør plads på telefonen ved at slette filer i programmets cachemappe. Adgang er normalt meget begrænset til systemprocesser.

OriginalText: Allows an application to get details about the currently synced feeds.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program får detaljer om de aktuelt synkroniserede feeds.

OriginalText: Allows an application to get the list of accounts known by the phone.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program henter listen over konti, der er kendt af telefonen.

OriginalText: Allows an application to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program starter selv, når systemet er færdig med at starte. Dette kan gøre starten af telefonen langsommere og generelt gøre telefonen langsommere ved altid at lade programmet køre.

OriginalText: Allows an application to install new or updated Android packages. Malicious applications can use this to add new applications with arbitrarily powerful permissions.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program installerer nye eller opdaterede Android-pakker. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at tilføje nye programmer med vilkårlige, effektive tilladelser.

OriginalText: Allows an application to kill background processes of other applications, even if memory isn\'t low.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at standse andre programmers baggrundsprocesser, selvom der ikke er mangel på hukommelse.

OriginalText: Allows an application to make calls to AccountAuthenticators
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program foretager opkald til kontogodkendere

OriginalText: Allows an application to make parts of itself persistent, so the system can\'t use it for other applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program gør dele af sig selv vedholdende, så systemet ikke kan bruge det til andre programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the APN settings, such as Proxy and Port of any APN.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer APN-indstillingerne, f.eks. enhver APNs Proxy og Port.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the Browser\'s geolocation permissions. Malicious applications can use this to allow sending location information to arbitrary web sites.
TranslatedText: Giver et program tilladelse til at ændre browserens tilladelser for geografisk placering. Skadelige programmer kan bruge dette til at tillade, at placeringsoplysninger sendes til vilkårlige websteder.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the Browser\'s history or bookmarks stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your Browser\'s data.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer browseroversigten eller bogmærker, der er gemt på din telefon. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at slette eller ændre din browsers data.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer kontaktdata (adresser), der er gemt på din telefon. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at slette eller ændre kontaktdata.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the Google services map. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer kortet over Google-tjenester. Ikke til brug til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the sync settings, such as whether sync is enabled for Contacts.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer indstillingerne for synkronisering, f.eks. kontakter skal synkroniseres.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the system\'s secure settings data. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer systemernes sikre indstillingsdata. Ikke til brug til almindelige programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify the system\'s settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system\'s configuration.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer systemets indstillingsdata. Ondsindede programmer kan skade systemets konfiguration.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify your currently synced feeds. This could allow a malicious application to change your synced feeds.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer dine aktuelle synkroniserede feeds. Dette kan muligvis lade et ondsindet program ændre dine synkroniserede feeds.

OriginalText: Allows an application to modify your preferred applications. This can allow malicious applications to silently change the applications that are run, spoofing your existing applications to collect private data from you.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer dine foretrukne programmer. Dette kan medføre, at ondsindede programmer ændrer kørende programmer i det skjulte og narrer dine eksisterende programmer til at indsamle personlige oplysninger fra dig.

OriginalText: Allows an application to monitor and control how the system launches activities. Malicious applications may completely compromise the system. This permission is only needed for development, never for normal phone usage.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program overvåger og kontrollerer, hvordan systemet starter aktiviteter. Ondsindede programmer kan fuldstændig kompromittere systemet. Denne tilladelse er kun nødvendig til udvikling, aldrig til normal telefonbrug.

OriginalText: Allows an application to move application resources from internal to external media and vice versa.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program flytter programressourcer fra interne til eksterne medier og omvendt.

OriginalText: Allows an application to move tasks to the foreground and background. Malicious applications can force themselves to the front without your control.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program flytter opgaver til forgrunden og baggrunden. Ondsindede programmer kan tvinge dem selv til forgrunden uden din kontrol.

OriginalText: Allows an application to perform operations like adding, and removing accounts and deleting their password.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program foretager handlinger, f.eks. at tilføje og fjerne konti samt slette sin adgangskode.

OriginalText: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program forhindrer telefonen i at gå i dvale.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read all of the calendar events stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your calendar events to other people.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser alle kalenderbegivenheder, der er gemt på din telefon. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at sende dine kalenderbegivenheder til andre mennesker.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser alle kontaktdata (adresser), der er gemt på din telefon. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at sende dine data til andre mennesker.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read and write the cache filesystem.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser og skriver til cache-filsystemet.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read and write to any resource owned by the diag group; for example, files in /dev. This could potentially affect system stability and security. This should be ONLY be used for hardware-specific diagnostics by the manufacturer or operator.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser og skriver til alle ressourcer, der ejes af diag-gruppen, som f.eks. filer i /dev. Dette kan muligvis påvirke systemets stabilitet og sikkerhed. Dette bør KUN bruges til hardwarespecifikke diagnosticeringer foretaget af producent eller udbyder.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read any private words, names and phrases that the user may have stored in the user dictionary.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser alle private ord, navne og sætninger, som brugeren eventuelt har gemt i brugerordbogen.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read from the system\'s various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser fra systemets forskellige logfiler. Dermed kan generelle oplysninger om, hvad du laver med telefonen, registreres, men logfilerne bør ikke indeholde personlige eller private oplysninger.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read the sync settings, such as whether sync is enabled for Contacts.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser synkroniseringsindstillingerne, f.eks. om kontakter skal synkroniseres.

OriginalText: Allows an application to read the sync stats; e.g., the history of syncs that have occurred.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser synkroniseringsstatistikker, f.eks. oversigten over forrige synkroniseringer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to receive packets not directly addressed to your device. This can be useful when discovering services offered near by. It uses more power than the non-multicast mode.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program modtager pakker, der ikke er direkte adresseret til din enhed. Dette kan være nyttigt, hvis du finder tjenester, der tilbydes i nærheden. Det bruger mere strøm end multicasttilstanden.

OriginalText: Allows an application to request authentication tokens.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program anmoder om godkendelsestokens

OriginalText: Allows an application to retrieve its code, data, and cache sizes
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program henter sin kode, data og cachestørrelser

OriginalText: Allows an application to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Malicious applications can make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program sender klæbende udsendelser, der bliver tilbage, efter udsendelsen er slut. Ondsindede programmer kan gøre telefonen langsom eller ustabil ved at få den til at bruge for meget hukommelse.

OriginalText: Allows an application to show system alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program viser vinduer med systemunderretninger. Ondsindede programmer kan overtage hele telefonens skærm.

OriginalText: Allows an application to turn on debugging for another application. Malicious applications can use this to kill other applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program slår fejlretning af andet program til. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at standse andre programmer.

OriginalText: Allows an application to use the account authenticator capabilities of the AccountManager, including creating accounts and getting and setting their passwords.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program bruger kontoadministratorens kontogodkendelsesegenskaber, bl.a. oprettelse af konti samt hentning og indstilling af deres adgangskoder.

OriginalText: Allows an application to use the SIP service to make/receive Internet calls.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at bruge SIP tjenesten til at ringe op via/modtage Internet opkald

OriginalText: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone, and to make and accept connections with paired devices.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program viser konfigurationen af den lokale Bluetooth-telefon samt opretter og accepterer forbindelse med parrede enheder.

OriginalText: Allows an application to view the information about the state of Wi-Fi.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program viser oplysninger om Wi-Fi-tilstanden.

OriginalText: Allows an application to view the information about the state of WiMAX.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at se information om WiMAX tilstand.

OriginalText: Allows an application to view the state of all networks.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program viser tilstanden for alle netværk.

OriginalText: Allows an application to write new words into the user dictionary.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program skriver nye ord i brugerordbogen.

OriginalText: Allows an application to write to the SD card.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program skriver til SD-kortet.

OriginalText: Allows application to access the audio record path.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program får adgang til lydregistreringsstien.

OriginalText: Allows application to disable the status bar or add and remove system icons.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet at deaktivere statuslinien eller tilføje og fjerne system ikoner

OriginalText: Allows application to expand or collapse the status bar.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program udvider eller skjuler statuslinjen.

OriginalText: Allows application to modify global audio settings such as volume and routing.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program ændrer globale lydindstillinger som f.eks. lydstyrke og kanalisering.

OriginalText: Allows application to process outgoing calls and change the number to be dialed. Malicious applications may monitor, redirect, or prevent outgoing calls.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program behandler udgående opkald og ændrer det nummer, der ringes til. Ondsindede programmer kan overvåge, omdirigere eller forhindre udgående opkald.

OriginalText: Allows application to read SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may read your confidential messages.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser sms-beskeder, der er gemt på din telefon eller dit SIM-kort. Ondsindede programmer kan eventuelt læse dine fortrolige beskeder.

OriginalText: Allows application to read the content of the frame buffer.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program læser indholdet fra rammebufferen.

OriginalText: Allows application to receive and process emergency broadcast messages. This permission is only available to system applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader applikation at modtage og bearbejde nødopkald. Denne tilladelse er kun mulig for system applikationer.

OriginalText: Allows application to receive and process MMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program modtager og behandler mms-beskeder. Ondsindede programmer kan overvåge dine beskeder eller slette dem uden at vise dem til dig.

OriginalText: Allows application to receive and process SMS messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program modtager og behandler sms-beskeder. Ondsindede programmer kan overvåge dine beskeder eller slette dem uden at vise dem til dig.

OriginalText: Allows application to receive and process WAP messages. Malicious applications may monitor your messages or delete them without showing them to you.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program modtager og behandler WAP-beskeder. Ondsindede programmer kan overvåge dine beskeder eller slette dem uden at vise dem til dig.

OriginalText: Allows application to request that the supplied signal be sent to all persistent processes.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet kan anmode om, at det leverede signal sendes til alle vedholdende processer.

OriginalText: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program henter oplysninger om nuværende og for nyligt kørende opgaver. Tillader, at eventuelt ondsindede programmer finder private oplysninger om andre programmer.

OriginalText: Allows application to retrieve internal state of the system. Malicious applications may retrieve a wide variety of private and secure information that they should never normally need.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program henter systemets interne tilstand. Ondsindede programmer kan hente en række private og sikre oplysninger, som de normalt aldrig bør have brug for.

OriginalText: Allows application to send SMS messages. Malicious applications may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program at sender sms-beskeder. Ondsindede programmer kan eventuelt koste dig penge ved at sende beskeder uden din bekræftelse.

OriginalText: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application at any time to collect images the camera is seeing.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet tager billeder med kameraet. Dette giver programmet mulighed for altid at indsamle de billeder, kameraet ser.

OriginalText: Allows application to use SurfaceFlinger low-level features.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program bruger SurfaceFlinger-funktioner på lavt niveau.

OriginalText: Allows application to write to SMS messages stored on your phone or SIM card. Malicious applications may delete your messages.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program skriver i sms-beskeder, der er gemt på din telefon eller dit SIM-kort. Ondsindede programmer kan eventuelt slette dine beskeder.

OriginalText: Allows applications to create and manage their own tokens, bypassing their normal Z-ordering. Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet opretter og administrerer sine egen tokens og gå uden om sin normale Z-rækkefølge. Bør aldrig være nødvendigt til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows applications to watch the keys you press even when interacting with another application (such as entering a password). Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program registrerer taster, du trykker på, selv når du interagerer med andre programmer (f.eks. ved indtastning af adgangskode). Bør aldrig være nødvendigt til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows enabling/disabling location update notifications from the radio. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader aktivering/deaktivering af placeringsdata fra radioen. Ikke til brug til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows read/write access to properties uploaded by the checkin service. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader læse/skrive-adgang til egenskaber, der er uploadet af kontroltjenesten. Ikke til brug til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and the like.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet får adgang til enhedens telefonfunktioner. Et program kan med denne tilladelse registrere denne telefons telefon- og serienummer, om et opkald er aktivt, nummeret som det opkald er forbundet til osv.

OriginalText: Allows the application to be the status bar.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program deaktiverer statuslinjen eller tilføjer eller fjerner systemikoner.

OriginalText: Allows the application to call any phone number, including emergency numbers, without your intervention. Malicious applications may place unnecessary and illegal calls to emergency services.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet ringer til alle telefonnumre inklusive nødnumre uden din indgriben. Ondsindede programmer kan eventuelt foretage unødvendige og ulovlige opkald til nødtjenester.

OriginalText: Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet ringer til telefonnumre uden din indgriben. Ondsindede programmer kan forårsage uventede opkald på din telefonregning. Vær opmærksom på, at programmet ikke kan ringe til nødnumre.

OriginalText: Allows the application to control the flashlight.
Allows the application to control the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can switch networks, turn the phone radio on and off and the like without ever notifying you.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet kontrollerer enhedens telefonfunktioner. Et program med denne tilladelse kan skifte netværk, slå telefonens radio til og fra og lignende uden nogensinde at informere dig.

OriginalText: Allows the application to control the system\'s backup and restore mechanism. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program kontrollerer systemets sikkerhedskopierings- og gendannelsesfunktion. Ikke til brug til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the application to control the vibrator.
Allows the application to control various peripherals for the purpose of hardware testing.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program kontrollerer forskellige perifere enheder for at teste hardwaren.

OriginalText: Allows the application to create secure storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet at oprette sikkert lager.

OriginalText: Allows the application to destroy secure storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet at ødelægge sikkert lager.

OriginalText: Allows the application to disable the entire phone permanently. This is very dangerous.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet deaktiverer hele telefonen permanent. Dette er meget farligt.

OriginalText: Allows the application to force the phone to reboot.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet tvinger telefonen til at genstarte.

OriginalText: Allows the application to format removable storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at et program formaterer flytbart lager.

OriginalText: Allows the application to get information on secure storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet at få oplysninger om sikkert lager.

OriginalText: Allows the application to manage preferences and permissions for USB devices.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet adgang til at håndtere indstillinger og tilladelser for USB enheder

OriginalText: Allows the application to mount / unmount secure storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet at montere/demontere sikkert lager.

OriginalText: Allows the application to mount and unmount filesystems for removable storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet monterer eller demonterer filsystemer til flytbar lagring.

OriginalText: Allows the application to read all the URLs that the Browser has visited, and all of the Browser\'s bookmarks.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet læser alle de webadresser, browseren har besøgt, og alle browserens bogmærker.

OriginalText: Allows the application to rename secure storage.
TranslatedText: Tillader programmet at omdøbe sikkert lager.

OriginalText: Allows the application to set an alarm in an installed alarm clock application. Some alarm clock applications may not implement this feature. an installed alarm clock application. Some alarm clock applications may not implement this feature.
TranslatedText: Tillader et program at indstille en alarm på en installeret alarm-ur\'s applikation. Nogle applikationer har muligvis ikke denne funktion

OriginalText: Allows the application to set the system wallpaper size hints.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet opsætter størrelsestip for systemets tapet.

OriginalText: Allows the application to set the system wallpaper.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet opsætter systemets tapet.

OriginalText: Allows the application to start CDMA provisioning. Malicious applications may unnecessarily start CDMA provisioning
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet starter CDMA-levering. Ondsindede programmer kan starte unødvendig CDMA-levering

OriginalText: Allows the application to tell the system which widgets can be used by which application. With this permission, applications can give access to personal data to other applications. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet fortæller systemet, hvilke widgets der kan bruges af hvilke programmer. Med denne tilladelse kan programmer give adgang til personlige oplysninger til andre programmer. Ikke til brug til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the application to turn the phone on or off.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at programmet slukker og tænder telefonen.

OriginalText: Allows the creation of windows that are intended to be used by the internal system user interface. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader oprettelse af vinduer, der er beregnet til at blive brugt af den interne systembrugergrænseflade. Ikke til brug for normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of a wallpaper. Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at brugeren forpligter sig til et tapets grænseflade på øverste niveau. Bør aldrig være nødvendig til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the holder to bind to the top-level interface of an input method. Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader, at brugeren forpligter sig til en inputmetodes grænseflade på øverste niveau. Bør aldrig være nødvendig til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the holder to send intents to a device administrator. Should never be needed for normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader brugeren at sende hensigter til en enhedsadministrator. Bør aldrig være nødvendigt for almindelige programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the modification of collected battery statistics. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader ændring af indsamlede batteristatistikker. Ikke til brug for normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows the modification of collected component usage statistics. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader ændring af indsamlede brugerstatistikker for komponenter. Ikke til brug til normale programmer.

OriginalText: Allows to invoke default container service to copy content. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader kald af standardcontainertjeneste for at kopiere indhold. Ikke til brug for almindelige programmer.

OriginalText: Allows to invoke default container service to copy content. Not for use by normal applications.
TranslatedText: Tillader kald af standardcontainertjeneste for at kopiere indhold. Ikke til brug for almindelige programmer.

OriginalText: Another application is already running that must be stopped before you can start a new one.
TranslatedText: En anden applikation kører allerede, denne skal stoppes før du kan starte en ny.

OriginalText: Are you sure you want to format the SD card? All data on your card will be lost.
TranslatedText: Er du sikker på, du ønsker at formatere SD-kortet? Alle data på kortet mistes.

OriginalText: Are you sure you wish to delete these resources?
Authentication via the proxy server was unsuccessful.
Automatically open AGPS, will switch off after 60 seconds of inactivity
TranslatedText: Tænd automatisk Mobil netværk AGPS, som vil slukke igen efter 60 sekunders inaktivitet

OriginalText: Before turning off USB storage, make sure you have unmounted (“ejected”) your Android‘s SD card from your computer.
TranslatedText: Sørg for, at du har demonteret (\udskubbet\") din Androids SD-kort fra computeren

OriginalText: By long press in text input to change later
TranslatedText: By long press in text input to change later

OriginalText: Caller ID defaults to not restricted. Next call: Not restricted
TranslatedText: Standarder for opkalds-id til ikke begrænset. Næste opkald: Ikke begrænset

TranslatedText: Standarder for opkalds-id til ikke begrænset. Næste opkald: Begrænset

OriginalText: Caller ID defaults to restricted. Next call: Not restricted
TranslatedText: Standarder for opkalds-id til begrænset. Næste opkald: Ikke begrænset

OriginalText: Caller ID defaults to restricted. Next call: Restricted
TranslatedText: Standarder for opkalds-id til begrænset. Næste opkald: Begrænset

OriginalText: Cannot sync time now for no network available, and it will be started when network is connected
TranslatedText: Kan ikke synkronisere tiden, da ingen tilgængelig netværksforbindelse er fundet, vil starte så snart forbindelse til netværket er oprettet

OriginalText: Clear default in Home Settings > Applications > Manage applications.
TranslatedText: Ryd standard i Startindstillinger > Programmer > Administrer programmer.

OriginalText: Connection problem or invalid feature code.
Connection problem or invalid MMI code.

TranslatedText: kontroller sikkerhedskopiering af system, og gendan

OriginalText: Control when device locks, requiring you re-enter its password.
TranslatedText: Kontrol når enheden låses, så du skal indtaste adgangskoden igen.

OriginalText: Create mock location sources for testing. Malicious applications can use this to override the location and/or status returned by real location sources such as GPS or Network providers or monitor and report your location to an external source.
TranslatedText: Opret imiterede placeringskilder til testning. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at tilsidesætte den returnerede placering og/eller status fra rigtige placeringskilder som f.eks. GPS eller netværksudbydere eller til at overvåge og rapportere din placering til en ekstern kilde.

OriginalText: Create mock location sources for testing. Malicious applications can use this to override the location and/or status returned by real location sources such as GPS or Network providers.
TranslatedText: Opret imiterede placeringskilder til testning. Ondsindede programmer kan bruge dette til at tilsidesætte den returnerede placering og/eller status fra rigtige placeringskilder som f.eks. GPS eller netværksudbydere.

OriginalText: Data traffic has reached the limit by %s
TranslatedText: Mobil data grænse tærskel overskredet med %sMB

OriginalText: Direct access to hardware on the handset.
TranslatedText: Direkte adgang til hardware på håndsættet.

OriginalText: Direct access to your contacts and calendar stored on the phone.
TranslatedText: Få direkte adgang til dine kontakter og din kalender, der er gemt på telefonen.
ring direkte op til alle telefonnumre

TranslatedText: Ønsker du, at browseren skal huske denne adgangskode?

OriginalText: Do you want to allow this request?
Do you want to enable the function of long-pressing the back key to kill the current process and its background services? \n\nEnable via Settings > System > Button Settings
TranslatedText: Vil du aktivere funktionen, at holde tilbage-knappen nede vil afslutte det kørende program og dets tilhørende baggrunds processor? \n\nAktiver via Indstillinger > System > Knap indstillinger

TranslatedText: Indtast PUK kode for at låse SIM kort op

Force your password to a new value, requiring the administrator give it to you before you can log in.
TranslatedText: Tving din adgangskode til en ny værdi. Dette kræver, at administratoren giver den til dig, før du kan kogge ind.

OriginalText: Going to exit.\nPlease reopen this app to refresh resource.
TranslatedText: Afslutter, genåbn for at genopfriske resourcelisten

OriginalText: Guard mode is turned on. Calls and text messages are hidden and launcher cannot enter editing mode.
TranslatedText: Hemmelig tilstand er aktiveret. Data er deaktiveret, Opkalds historik, email, noter og beskeder er skjulte, og skrivebords opsætningen kan ikke ændres

OriginalText: If you turn on USB storage, some applications you are using will stop and may be unavailable until you turn off USB storage.
TranslatedText: Hvis du slår USB-lagring til, vil nogle af de programmer, som du bruger, stoppe, og de kan være utilgængelige, indtil du slår USB-lagring til igen.

OriginalText: In guarded mode, calls and text messages will be hidden and launcher will not be able to enter editing mode.
TranslatedText: I hemmelig tilstand, vil opkalds historik, beskeder og data blive deaktiveret. Aktiver hemmelig tilstand?
